# [_z_][z] Plugin for [Oh My Fish][omf-link] that brings [z], the jump around utility, to Fish. ## Install ```fish $ omf install z ``` The upstream script will be installed and updated automatically with the Oh My Fish plugin. No additional configuration is needed.
